             sworn.</p>
               <p>I am servant to Mr. Pugh; the prisoner was making himself ready to go to his work; the men were going to load the cart at the door, I went with them; as soon as the prisoner saw us all together, he went up into his room, and I suspected that he had taken some soap up stairs.</p>
               <p>Prisoner. I leave my defence to my country.(Five witnesses were called by the prisoner, who gave him a good character for honesty and industry.)</p>
               <p>GUILTY, (Aged 32.)</p>
